{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you live under-- under a constant dehumanized condition, where-- where death-- death is a relief, if people act the way they act, you-- you-- you can find some kind of a-- some kind of a, not justification, but you can find some understanding why they act the way they do.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed in Flossenburg [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGH] about a week or 10 days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, I don't think it was 10 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lucky-- we considered ourselves lucky to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were loaded up on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It turned out that they were taking us to Hersbruck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hersbruck was a subcamp from Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And in-- in Hersbruck, we came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, it took-- it's a very short distance from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hersbruck is very close to-- to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It shouldn't-- it shouldn't have taken more than a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Why the-- the-- the trains went-- went so-- so long, they went a few miles and then they stopped for hours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was, I think, because the rail lines were-- were interrupted, broken off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had to wait for-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, when we got into Hersbruck, so it-- I think it was around January the 5th.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It might be fifth or sixth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I I am not so sure now, but it couldn't-- it couldn't be-- it couldn't have been any-- any much later.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we got into Hersbruck, and in that camp, we came in, it was very clean.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't describe the-- what it looks-- what the-- the beds look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In every camp was the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Those were bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
